<div class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">How to Use This RPE Calculator</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The tool has three separate modes, each accessible from the tab buttons at the top. They're designed to handle different situations, so here's a quick walkthrough of all three.</p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-6 mb-2">Tab 1: Find Your Working Weight (Weight from RPE)</h3>
