  </div>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-6 mb-2">Tab 2: Estimate Your 1RM from a Recent Set</h3>
  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">This one works backwards from something that already happened. It's especially handy for lifters who've never actually tested their 1RM, or who want a current estimate without doing an all-out max attempt mid-training block.</p>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4">
    <li>Enter the weight that was lifted.</li>
    <li>Enter the number of reps completed.</li>
